    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Gateway errors / min",
      "description": "EventError emissions by subsystem. Drill into Reliability \u2192 Gateway errors by subsystem/code.\n\ncovered_by:\n  - defenseclaw_gateway_errors \u2192 internal/telemetry/gateway_events.go (EventError)",
